You are here: SALESFORCE HELP > DOCS > SERVICE CLOUD > Open Messaging

Access Messaging through the Service Console app that your admin set up. Log into Omni-Channel to start chatting with customers.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience.
This article applies to: 
Messaging for In-App, Messaging for Web, standard and enhanced WhatsApp, standard and enhanced Facebook Messenger, standard and enhanced SMS, enhanced Apple Messages for Business, and Bring Your Own Channel

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To send and receive messages in Messaging for In-App and Web:	
Messaging for In-App and Web permission set license AND 
Messaging for In-App and Web user permission

To send and receive messages in standard and enhanced Messaging channels:	Messaging Agent

Open the app that contains Messaging. To open the App Launcher, click . Click the app that contains Messaging. Log into Omni-Channel. Messages are routed only to agents who are logged in.
